overview: Promi Big Brother - Die Late Night Show is a live late-night show that has been broadcast on sixx from August 2014 to August 2020 and on Sat.1 since August 2021 as part of the Promi Big Brotherprogram. During the first season, the show ran under the title Promi Big Brother - Late Night Live.
